    "summary": "<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">九疑山国家森林公园， 位于湖南省南部永州市<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/baike.so.com\/doc\/4191623-4392353.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">宁远县<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">境内，宁远县城南60里，是国家级文物保护单位、国家AAAA级旅游景区、湖南省首批重点<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/baike.so.com\/doc\/5660482-5873133.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">风景名胜区<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">、省自然保护区，以<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/baike.so.com\/doc\/7714478-7988573.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">文物古迹<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">、自然风光、溶洞和民俗风情著称于世，系湖南省六大风景名胜区，十大旅游区之一。其中的九疑山，又名<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/baike.so.com\/doc\/4024277-4221730.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">苍梧山<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">，属<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/baike.so.com\/doc\/423357-448331.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">南岭<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">山脉之<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/baike.so.com\/doc\/5909880-6122786.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">萌渚岭<\/span><\/a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none;\">，纵横2000余里，南接罗浮，北连衡岳。<\/span><\/p>",
