    "traffic": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">（1）自驾：从海口出发进入G98至兴隆出口，沿指示牌开至兴隆\/石梅湾出口出来，继续直行至兴梅大道，向右转至兴隆旅游开发区，康乐园酒店旁即是康乐园大剧场；<\/span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"\/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">（2）动车：游客若从海口机场或市区出发，可以乘坐海口—三亚的高铁动车；若从三亚出发，可以乘坐三亚—海口的高铁动车；<\/span><br style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"\/><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">（3）公交：万宁高铁车站有到东山岭文化旅游区的8路公交车。<\/span><\/p>",
